  "texts": [
    "There are two types of object detectors: one-stage and two-stage detectors.",
    "Detectron2 is a two-stage system, and the detection task is carried out in two steps.",
    "The first step is to extract the region of interest (RoI).",
    "The second step involves target classification and positioning.",
    "The nature of these two-stage detectors makes them slower than one-stage detectors such as YOLO and SSD, but they can produce more accurate results."
  ],
